---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import IdentityIndex from '../components/IdentityIndex.astro';
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro';
import SiteHeader from '../components/SiteHeader.astro';
import { identityProfiles } from '../data/methods.mjs';
import { methodBySlug } from '../data/methods.mjs';
import { positioning } from '../data/portfolio.mjs';
---

<Layout title="关于｜Anonymousyz" description="Anonymousyz 的工作经历、常做的事情、公开范围和联系方式。" image="/og/about.png">
  <SiteHeader current="about" />

  <main>
    <section class="editorial-hero shell">
      <p class="editorial-eyebrow">关于</p>
      <h1>{positioning[0]}，<br />{positioning[1]}</h1>
      <p class="editorial-lead">过去八年，我做过产业研究、政策分析和重大项目，也参与过产品设计与软件建设。</p>
    </section>

    <section class="editorial-section shell identity-section" id="identity" aria-labelledby="identity-title">
      <div class="editorial-section__head">
        <h2 id="identity-title">身份</h2>
      </div>
      <IdentityIndex identities={identityProfiles} />
    </section>

    <section class="editorial-section shell about-editorial">
      <h2>我经常接手两类工作</h2>
      <div>
        <p>一类工作材料很多，还不能据此作出判断；另一类已经有明确的业务目标，需要落成产品和软件。</p>
        <div class="about-inline-links">
          <a href="/methods/research-and-judgment/">{methodBySlug['research-and-judgment'].title} <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="editorial-section shell about-editorial">
      <h2>我在项目里做什么</h2>
      <div>
        <p>项目前期，我做研究、政策分析、方案和申报材料；进入建设阶段后，继续梳理角色、流程、数据和权限，参与产品定义、测试和交付检查。</p>
        <div class="about-inline-links">
          <a href="/projects/#industrial-energy-carbon-system">工业绿色微电网评价软件 <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
          <a href="/projects/#industrial-digital-public-service-platform">工业技术改造投资管理平台项目 <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="editorial-section shell about-editorial">
      <h2>公开内容</h2>
      <div>
        <p>网站只收录公开仓库和脱敏后的项目记录。客户身份、原始材料、真实数据、账号、运行地址和私有代码不在公开范围内。</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="editorial-section shell about-editorial">
      <h2>联系</h2>
      <div>
        <p>如要讨论研究如何支持决策，或怎样把一项业务做成可用的软件，可以在 GitHub 联系我。</p>
        <div class="about-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/Anonymousyz" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <SiteFooter />
</Layout>
